<div id="top-content">
  <div class="heading-with-actions top-heading">
    <h1>
      <span translate="no">xmerl_eventp</span> 
      <small class="app-vsn" translate="no">(xmerl v2.1.9)</small>

    </h1>




      <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/xmerl/src/xmerl_eventp.erl#L23" title="View Source" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow">
        <i class="ri-code-s-slash-line" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <span class="sr-only">View Source</span>
      </a>

  </div>


    <section id="moduledoc">
<p>Simple event-based processors (front-ends to <a href="xmerl_scan.html"><code class="inline">xmerl_scan</code></a>).</p><p>Implements processing XML documents in streams for parsing in SAX style.</p><p>Each front-end contains more elaborate settings of
<a href="xmerl_scan.html"><code class="inline">xmerl_scan</code></a> that makes usage of the customization functions.</p>
    </section>

</div>

