              <h1 class="signature" translate="no">file_sax(Fname, CallBackModule, UserState, Options)<span class="signature-arrow">&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;</span><span class="signature-result">NewUserState</span></h1>





          <a href="https://github.com/erlang/otp/blob/master/lib/xmerl/src/xmerl_eventp.erl#L197" class="icon-action" rel="help nofollow" aria-label="View Source">
