            <pre translate="no">Options = <a href="#t:option_list/0">option_list</a>()</pre>

            <pre translate="no">Result = {<a href="xmerl_scan.html#t:document/0">xmerl_scan:document</a>(), Rest} | {error, Reason}</pre>

        </div>


<p>Parse file containing an XML document as a stream, SAX style.</p><p>Wrapper for a call to the XML parser <a href="xmerl_scan.html"><code class="inline">xmerl_scan</code></a> with
a <a href="xmerl_scan.html#t:option_list/0"><code class="inline">continuation_fun</code></a> for handling
streams of XML data.  Note that the <code class="inline">continuation_fun</code>, <code class="inline">acc_fun</code>,
<code class="inline">fetch_fun</code>, <code class="inline">rules</code>, <code class="inline">hook_fun</code>, <code class="inline">close_fun</code> and <code class="inline">user_state</code> options
cannot be user defined using this parser.</p>
  </section>
</section>
